body:
@printdhruv Thank you for your response, however, maybe I was not really clear about the problem. 

The issue is that the window to select the saved bookmark does not even appear when clicking on it:

[link](http://i.imgur.com/knERIxg.gif)

The saved bookmark only has 21k vectors (with 300 dimensions), so not that big I suppose. The weird thing is that everything worked perfectly a month ago.

In terms of saving and loading, I just used default settings.
